  <brief_title>Conservative Treatment of Proximal Humeral Fractures</brief_title>
  <official_title>Conservative Treatment of Proximal Humeral Fractures - Immobilization for 1 Week Compared to Three Weeks: Prospective Randomized Study</official_title>
